Package me.marcosassuncao.servsim.scheduler

Class DefaultScheduler

java.lang.Object
me.marcosassuncao.servsim.SimEntity
me.marcosassuncao.servsim.scheduler.AbstractScheduler
me.marcosassuncao.servsim.scheduler.DefaultScheduler
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventSink<SimEvent>, ListenerService<WorkUnitEvent,EventListener<WorkUnitEvent>>, Scheduler
public class DefaultScheduler extends AbstractScheduler
This class implements a simple scheduler where the waiting queue can be ordered in different ways. If no sorting comparator is provided, the scheduler will present a FIFO behaviour.
Author:
Marcos Dias de Assuncao
